Class RuleMetaData

  • java.lang.Object
    • hcl.epitrack.ontologygenerator.properties.RuleMetaData

  • public class RuleMetaData
extends java.lang.Object
    RuleMetaData objects describe particular data to apply XLSXMappingRules object Notice that this class is independant to the XLSX rule description (no rule id control) and is unmutable (private setter method)
